---
---

<section class="section-insight" aria-labelledby="insight-h2">
  <div class="insight-inner">
    <span class="pill pill-blue story-element" data-story-delay="0">A virada</span>
    <h2 class="insight-h2 story-element" id="insight-h2" data-story-delay="1">
      E se ao acordar,<br />
      você já soubesse<br />
      <span class="blue">exatamente quem visitar?</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="insight-divider" id="insightDivider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <p class="insight-text story-element" data-story-delay="3">
      O MediVisitas analisa sua carteira e sugere automaticamente quem visitar baseado em potencial de prescrição e tempo sem visita. Você só precisa seguir a agenda.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-insight {
    min-height: 80vh;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 120px clamp(24px, 5vw, 80px);
  }

  .insight-inner {
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .insight-h2 {
    font-size: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 0.95;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .insight-h2 .blue {
    color: var(--color-blue);
  }

  .insight-divider {
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--color-blue);
    width: 60px;
    margin: 40px auto;
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transform-origin: center;
    transition: transform 600ms cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .insight-divider:global(.revealed) {
    transform: scaleX(1);
  }

  .insight-text {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--color-ink-secondary);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
</style>
